snippet.title: Sporting KC vs Inter Miami | 2025 Concacaf Champions Cup | Round One
snippet.description:
üìπ Game Highlights

Sporting KC üÜö Inter Miami

#ChampionsCup #concacaf #intermiami #sportingkc #roundone #highlights

 Inter Miami CF earned a 1-nil victory against Sporting Kansas City in the first leg of their Round One Series as the 2025 Concacaf Champions Cup continued Wednesday at Children‚Äôs Mercy Park in Kansas City, Kansas.

The clearest chances in the first half were courtesy of the visitors, with Luis Su√°rez being just wide of the mark with an attempt from inside the box in the 8‚Äô and a long-range right-footed drive in the 38‚Äô. 

Inter Miami found the opener in the 56‚Äô through Lionel Messi, who sent the ball to the back of the net with a right-footed finish inside the box to capitalize on a precise long-ball delivered by Sergio Busquets. 

Messi‚Äôs goal against Sporting Kansas City was his first right-footed goal in continental club competition since doing so in the UEFA Champions League with FC Barcelona in 2019 against Manchester United.

Seventeen of Sergio Busquets‚Äô last 29 assists in all club competitions for FC Barcelona and Inter Miami set up goals scored by Lionel Messi, dating back to March 2016.

Lionel Messi has been involved in 66 goals (52 goals, 14 assists) in 81 career knockout stage matches in continental competitions (UEFA Champions League and Concacaf Champions Cup), including at least one goal involvement in all four of his appearances in the Concacaf Champions Cup (3 goals, 2 assists).

√ìscar Ustari stood out in goal for the Herons, registering three saves to collect his first clean sheet of the campaign. 

The victory marks the first away win for Inter Miami in the Concacaf Champions Cup.

Erick Thommy attempted seven dribbles against Inter Miami, the most for a Sporting Kansas City player in a Concacaf Champions Cup match since 2016, equaling Yohan Croizet‚Äôs against Independiente La Chorrera and Gerso against Monterrey in 2019.

The two clubs will meet again next Tuesday in Florida for their second-leg match. The aggregate winner will advance to the Round of 16.

snippet.title: Gol Spektakuler Nick dan David Bawa Pulang 1 Poin dari Persija | Match Highlights Persija 2-2 PERSIB
snippet.description:
PERSIB berhasil menggagalkan pesta kemenangan Persija Jakarta setelah memaksakan hasil imbang 2-2 kepada Persija Jakarta pada pertandingan pekan ke-23 Liga 1 2023/2024 di Stadion Patriot Candrabhaga, Kota Bekasi, Minggu, 16 Februari 2025.

PERSIB sempat tertinggal dua gol di babak pertama melalui gol Gustavo Almeida menit 33 dan Firza Andika menit 38. Namun, PERSIB bangkit di babak kedua dengan mencetak dua gol balasan melalui Nick Kuipers menit 62 dan David da Silva menit 70.

Selain melanjutkan catatan tak terkalahkan di laga tandang, hasil imbang ini mengokohkan posisi PERSIB di puncak klasemen dengan mengumpulkan nilai 50, hasil 14 kali menang, 8 imbang dan sekali kalah. PERSIB unggul 9 poin dari Persebaya Surabaya.
____________

#PERSIB #PERSIBTV #WeArePERSIB

snippet.title: Suzuki APV baru 2025
snippet.description:
Siapa tak kenal Suzuki APV? Ini adalah mobil legendaris Suzuki yang didaulat sebagai pengganti Suzuki Carry untuk melawan dominasi Avanza-Xenia.

Bedanya, jika Avanza dan Xenia sudah berubah hingga tiga generasi, Suzuki APV tidak berubah banyak meski umurnya telah menginjak 21 tahun. Kira-kira apa ada bedanya antara Suzuki APV tahun 2025 dibanding APV yang kalian kenal? Simak penjelasan reviewer AutonetMagz, @HillariusSatrio berikut ini, langsung dari IIMS 2025.

snippet.title: IIMS 2025: Ada Apa Saja?
snippet.description:
IIMS (Indonesi International Motor Show) merupakan pameran otomotif di Indonesia dan di tahun ini berlangsung dari 13 - 23 Februari 2025 di JIEXPO Kemayoran, Jakarta.

Pada video kali ini, reviewer OtoDriver, Fitra Eri dan Luthfi Aziz mengunjungi pameran di hari pertama khusus pers dan VIP, sebelum publik diizinkan masuk. Di sini kami tunjukkan pada Anda, apa saja mobil baru dan konsep yang dapat Anda saksikan di sana.

Silakan juga sambangi website kami, www.otodriver.com untuk berita terkini dan paling menarik seputar dunia otomotif. Di sana juga Anda bisa melihat review mobil-mobil terkini yang dilakukan oleh reviewer berpengalaman kami. Selain itu di www.OtoDriver.Com Anda juga dapat melakukan komparasi sendiri antar-merek mobil. 

Jangan lupa klik Like bila Anda menyukai video ini, juga isi Comment tentang mobil ini atau kritik untuk perbaikan kami ke depannya. Jangan lupa juga SHARE video ini ke teman-teman Anda yang mungkin sedang membutuhkan informasi mengenai mobil.

Subscribe Channel Youtube kami di https://www.youtube.com/otodriver
Untuk yang memiliki akun FB bisa follow kami di https://www.facebook.com/otodriver dan https://twitter.com/otodriver.

Selamat menyaksikan, semoga menghibur dan membantu Anda menentukan pilihan mobil.

snippet.title: LAGI LAGI TENIS INTERNASIONAL PRESENTED BY PERTAMINA
snippet.description:
Lagi-lagi Tenis Internasional adalah ajang sportainment spektakuler yang mempertemukan selebritas top Indonesia dan Korea Selatan dalam pertandingan tenis penuh hiburan. Setelah sukses besar di tahun 2023, RANS Sportainment kembali menghadirkan acara ini dengan skala lebih besar dan format lebih mendunia.

Digelar pada Minggu, 9 Februari 2025 di Tennis Indoor Senayan, Jakarta, acara ini akan dipandu oleh Andre Taulany dan Sheryl Sheinafia, serta dimeriahkan oleh penampilan spesial dari Maliq & D‚ÄôEssentials.

Tim Indonesia yang diperkuat Raffi Ahmad, Nagita Slavina, Desta Mahendra, Nia Ramadhani, dan Dikta Wicaksono akan berhadapan dengan bintang Korea Selatan seperti Park Eun Seok, Hong Soo Ah, Choi Woong, Jung Ha Young, dan Tae Yun.

Dengan kombinasi olahraga, hiburan, dan bintang lintas negara, Lagi-lagi Tenis Internasional siap menjadi perhelatan sportainment paling dinanti di awal tahun 2025!

snippet.title: SOBAT NGARIT PRANK BELI NMAX TURBO 2025
snippet.description:
Pencari Rumput PRANK BELI NMAX TURBO 2025 SEPERTI INI REAKSI MARKETING YAMAHA 


Halo sahabat semua, di video kali ini kami tim Youtube Indonesia Ekspos membuat konten Social Experiment (Prank) Sobat Ngarit beli motor Nmax Turbo 2025 dengan uang cash atau tunai disertai pakaian gembel atau baju gelandang pencari rumput masuk ke Dealer Sepeda Motor Yamaha Panggung Motor di jalan raya Sukowati atau Jl. Maospati - Solo No.161-171, Kebayan 3, Sragen Kulon, Kec. Sragen, Kabupaten Sragen, Jawa Tengah 57212

Tanpa disadari pegawai deler Yamaha Panggung Motor Sragen Sobat ngarit beli motor Yamaha Nmax Turbo dengan membawa karung berisi rumput bercampur uang tunai pada hari Jumat 7 Februari 2025.

Pemilik Video : Khoiri ( Mas Jebleh Youtuber ).
Sales Marketing Yamaha kena prank bernama Putri
Cameraman : Huri Yanto

snippet.title: Jurassic World Rebirth | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A new era is born. Watch the Jurassic World Rebirth trailer now. 

-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@jurassicworld
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jurassicworld
X: https://twitter.com/jurassicworld
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jurassicworld
Official Site: https://www.jurassicworld.com/

A new era is born. This summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey and two-time Oscar¬Æ winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an extraction team race to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park, inhabited by the worst of the worst that were left behind. 

Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planet‚Äôs ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air within that tropical biosphere hold, in their DNA, the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy Award¬Æ nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure the genetic material. When Zora‚Äôs operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on a forbidden island that had once housed an undisclosed research facility for Jurassic Park. There, in a terrain populated by dinosaurs of vastly different species, they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that has been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zora‚Äôs most trusted team member; Critics Choice and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reuben‚Äôs family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebs‚Äô crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by Oscar¬Æ nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of last summer‚Äôs blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

A new era is born. This summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey and two-time Oscar¬Æ winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an extraction team race to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park, inhabited by the worst of the worst that were left behind. 

Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planet‚Äôs ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air within that tropical biosphere hold, in their DNA, the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy Award¬Æ nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure the genetic material. When Zora‚Äôs operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on a forbidden island that had once housed an undisclosed research facility for Jurassic Park. There, in a terrain populated by dinosaurs of vastly different species, they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that has been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zora‚Äôs most trusted team member; Critics Choice and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reuben‚Äôs family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebs‚Äô crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by Oscar¬Æ nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of last summer‚Äôs blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

snippet.title: Rizwan Fadilah, Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
#RizwanFadilah #NabilaTaqiyyah #Taksatucerita

Dengarkan Rizwan Fadilah & Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita

Lagu ini bercerita tentang hubungan penuh makna antara sepasang kekasih yang dulu saling mencintai. Namun, seiring waktu, perbedaan mulai muncul, menciptakan jarak di antara mereka. Percakapan yang dulu penuh pengertian berubah menjadi perdebatan, dan kebiasaan yang dulu indah kini menjadi penghalang. Mereka akhirnya menyadari bahwa tujuan hidup dan impian mereka berbeda, sehingga memutuskan untuk melepaskan satu sama lain demi kebaikan bersama, meski masih saling mencintai.
Sebelum resmi berduet dalam lagu ‚ÄúTAK SATU CERITA‚Äù, Rizwan Fadilah dan Nabila Taqiyyah telah lebih dulu berkolaborasi dengan saling menyanyikan lagu satu sama lain, yang berhasil mendapatkan respons positif dari para penonton. Rizwan dan Nabila pun mengungkapkan rasa bahagia atas terwujudnya duet ini, terutama karena keduanya menyukai lagu tersebut dan merasa vokal mereka berpadu dengan baik. Proses penulisan dan rekaman lagu ini berlangsung menyenangkan dengan banyak diskusi kreatif di antara keduanya. Salah satu momen yang paling berkesan bagi mereka adalah saat pembuatan video musik, di mana mereka saling beradu peran dengan penuh semangat.

localized.title: Rizwan Fadilah, Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita (Official Music Video)
localized.description:
#RizwanFadilah #NabilaTaqiyyah #Taksatucerita

Dengarkan Rizwan Fadilah & Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita

Lagu ini bercerita tentang hubungan penuh makna antara sepasang kekasih yang dulu saling mencintai. Namun, seiring waktu, perbedaan mulai muncul, menciptakan jarak di antara mereka. Percakapan yang dulu penuh pengertian berubah menjadi perdebatan, dan kebiasaan yang dulu indah kini menjadi penghalang. Mereka akhirnya menyadari bahwa tujuan hidup dan impian mereka berbeda, sehingga memutuskan untuk melepaskan satu sama lain demi kebaikan bersama, meski masih saling mencintai.
Sebelum resmi berduet dalam lagu ‚ÄúTAK SATU CERITA‚Äù, Rizwan Fadilah dan Nabila Taqiyyah telah lebih dulu berkolaborasi dengan saling menyanyikan lagu satu sama lain, yang berhasil mendapatkan respons positif dari para penonton. Rizwan dan Nabila pun mengungkapkan rasa bahagia atas terwujudnya duet ini, terutama karena keduanya menyukai lagu tersebut dan merasa vokal mereka berpadu dengan baik. Proses penulisan dan rekaman lagu ini berlangsung menyenangkan dengan banyak diskusi kreatif di antara keduanya. Salah satu momen yang paling berkesan bagi mereka adalah saat pembuatan video musik, di mana mereka saling beradu peran dengan penuh semangat.

snippet.description:

Saksikan kisah legendaris dari tanah Aceh tentang Tuan Tapa, penghuni pertama sebuah pulau yang damai. Di pulau yang masih asri ini, kehidupannya berubah saat bertemu sepasang naga dari negeri China yang diusir karena tak memiliki keturunan. Kebaikan hati sang raksasa membuat ia menerima kedua naga tersebut untuk tinggal di tepi pantai pulaunya.

Kasih sayang dapat tumbuh pada siapapun
